<template>
 
</template>

<script>
import MediaCard from '@/items/MediaCard.vue';

export default {
  name: 'HelloWorld',
  props: {
    msg: String,
  },
  components: {
  	MediaCard,
  },
};



	function request(action, success, data = {}) {
		data.api_key = this.key;

		$.ajax({
			url : 'proxy.php',
			data: data,
			dataType: "json",

			beforeSend: request => {
				request.setRequestHeader("X-Proxy-URL", this.url + this.version + action);
			},

			success: success,

			error: function() {
				if(window.debug) {
					console.log(action + ' error', arguments);
				}
			}
		});
	}
</script>

}
